      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>BINDLEY WESTERN INDUSTRIES, Indianapolis, a wholesale distributor of drugs, and health and beauty aids, said it had completed the purchase of the assets of Kendall Drug Company, Shelby, N.C.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>BINDLEY WESTERN INDUSTRIES, Indianapolis, a wholesale distributor of drugs, and health and beauty aids, said it had completed the purchase of the assets of Kendall Drug Company, Shelby, N.C.</p>
        <p>RADIATION CARE INC., Atlanta, an operator of radiation therapy centers, said it would sell 17 centers and certain corporate assets to Oncology Therapies Inc., for $27 million. Radiation's four remaining diagnostic imaging centers would be merged with a new company controlled by its chairman, Thomas Haire.</p>
      </block>
